description.narrative: 361,168 children in humanitarian situation are accessing formal or non-formal education through UNICEF's support. 835,871 children have also been provided with individual education/early learning materials. Teaching at the Right Level (TaRL) is found to be a viable remedial approach that supports learners with reading and numeracy deficiencies. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
